  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd6\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da9\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A petition from Wasantha that fundamental rights were violated",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Wasantha Mudalige, the convener of the Inter-University Student Power Council, filed a fundamental rights petition before the Supreme Court today (26) stating that his fundamental rights were violated by being detained on detention orders against the law.",
        "Six persons, including the Inspector General of Police and the Director of the Criminal Investigation Department, have been named as respondents in this petition filed by lawyer Manjula Balasuriya.",
        "The complainant has mentioned in his petition that he was illegally arrested by the security forces on the 18th of August and kept in custody on the orders of the Minister of Defense, President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "The petitioner has submitted in his petition that he is studying archeology at Rajarata University and is an active fighter in the Gota Go village struggle and has actively contributed to many social issues in the country as a student activist.",
        "Due to this, the petitioner has requested in his petition that this petition be heard and an order be issued stating that his fundamental rights have been violated and an order be issued to allow his family relatives and a lawyer to visit him.",
        "Also, the petitioner has requested the Supreme Court in his petition to cancel the detention orders and issue an order to release him."
      ],
